Package: hifiberry-eeprom
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         ${python3:Depends},
         python3-libgpiod,
         gpiod
Suggests: raspi-utils-eeprom
Description: HiFiBerry EEPROM tools
 EEPROM files and tools for HiFiBerry HAT boards.
 Contains pre-compiled EEPROM images for various HiFiBerry products
 and the hateeprom library for reading/writing HAT EEPROMs.
 .
 This package provides:
  - Pre-compiled EEPROM images for HiFiBerry products
  - hateeprom command-line tool for EEPROM manipulation
  - Python library for HAT EEPROM access via bitbang I2C
 .
 Files are installed to /usr/share/hifiberry-eeprom/.
